      "id": "X_F4zeQRiibZybPQzqJj9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1569.5219828287761,
      "y": -44.93489583333326,
      "width": 650.4996948242188,
      "height": 525,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0D",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 155807198,
      "version": 46,
      "versionNonce": 1193146846,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777296384596,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | File Header (100 bytes) - Page 1 ONLY     |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | Page Header (Header)                         | <- Fixed position\n    |   - 8 bytes for leaf nodes                   |\n    |   - 12 bytes for interior nodes              |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | Cell Pointer Array (Ptr Array)                | <- Low to High\n    |   - 2 bytes per pointer                        |    (Ordered)\n    |   - Sorted by key value                        |\n    |                      |                              |\n    |                      v                             |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | Unallocated Space (Gap)                     |\n    |                      ^                             |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | Cell Content Area (Content)                      | <- High to Low\n    |   - Cells packed tightly                         |    (Unordered)\n    |   - May contain freeblock list                   |\n    |   - May contain fragmented space                 |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | File Header (100 bytes) - Page 1 ONLY     |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | Page Header (Header)                         | <- Fixed position\n    |   - 8 bytes for leaf nodes                   |\n    |   - 12 bytes for interior nodes              |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | Cell Pointer Array (Ptr Array)                | <- Low to High\n    |   - 2 bytes per pointer                        |    (Ordered)\n    |   - Sorted by key value                        |\n    |                      |                              |\n    |                      v                             |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | Unallocated Space (Gap)                     |\n    |                      ^                             |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+\n    | Cell Content Area (Content)                      | <- High to Low\n    |   - Cells packed tightly                         |    (Unordered)\n    |   - May contain freeblock list                   |\n    |   - May contain fragmented space                 |\n    +--------------------------------------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Oo3ssIJOHF6Up3X2XMln7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1568.8059895833333,
      "y": 1.7122395833333712,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 700,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0E",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1933512222,
      "version": 128,
      "versionNonce": 1238842078,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777296466525,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "┌─────────────────────┐\n│ File Header (100 Bytes) - Page 1 Only     │\n├─────────────────────┤\n│ Page Header                                     | ← Fixed Position\n│   - Page type                        8 Bytes  | ← 8 Bytes for leaf nodes\n│     - Page Type Flags               1 Byte   |\n│     - First Freeblock Offset       2 Bytes  |\n│     - Number of Cells                2 Bytes  |\n│     - Cell Content Area Start      2 Bytes |\n│     - Fragmented Bytes Count     1 Byte   |\n│   - Right-most child pointer        4 Bytes  │ ← + 4 Bytes for interior nodes\n├─────────────────────┤\n│ Cell Pointer Array                        │ ← Grow from low to high address\n│   - Each pointer: 2 Bytes                 │   (Ordered)\n│   - Sorted by key value                   │\n│              ↓                            │\n├───────────────────────────────────────\n────┤\n│ Unallocated Space                         │\n│              ↑                            │\n├───────────────────────────────────────\n────┤\n│ Cell Content Area                         │ ← Grow from high to low address\n│   - Densely arranged cells                │   (Unordered)\n│   - May contain freeblock linked list     │\n│   - May contain fragment space            │\n└───────────────────────────────────────\n────┘",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "┌─────────────────────┐\n│ File Header (100 Bytes) - Page 1 Only     │\n├─────────────────────┤\n│ Page Header                                     | ← Fixed Position\n│   - Page type                        8 Bytes  | ← 8 Bytes for leaf nodes\n│     - Page Type Flags               1 Byte   |\n│     - First Freeblock Offset       2 Bytes  |\n│     - Number of Cells                2 Bytes  |\n│     - Cell Content Area Start      2 Bytes |\n│     - Fragmented Bytes Count     1 Byte   |\n│   - Right-most child pointer        4 Bytes  │ ← + 4 Bytes for interior nodes\n├─────────────────────┤\n│ Cell Pointer Array                        │ ← Grow from low to high address\n│   - Each pointer: 2 Bytes                 │   (Ordered)\n│   - Sorted by key value                   │\n│              ↓                            │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Unallocated Space                         │\n│              ↑                            │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Cell Content Area                         │ ← Grow from high to low address\n│   - Densely arranged cells                │   (Unordered)\n│   - May contain freeblock linked list     │\n│   - May contain fragment space            │\n└───────────────────────────────────────────┘",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "glBT3yv8oF0VaNtLUBtAa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1133.4655980335097,
      "y": 295.358695089195,
      "width": 762.3197631835938,
      "height": 675,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0F",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 681562498,
      "version": 451,
      "versionNonce": 2037525698,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777861909742,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    +-----------------------------------------------------------+\n    | File Header (100 Bytes) - Page 1 Only               |\n    +------------------------------------------------------------+\n    | Page Header                                               | <- Fixed Position\n    |                                                               |\n    |   - Page type ......................................... 8 Bytes      | <- Leaf pages\n    |       - Page Type Flags ........................... 1 Byte     |\n    |       - First Freeblock Offset ................ 2 Bytes   |\n    |       - Number of Cells ............................. 2 Bytes   |\n    |       - Cell Content Area Start .............. 2 Bytes   |\n    |       - Fragmented Bytes Count ............. 1 Byte     |\n    |   - Right-most child pointer ................. 4 Bytes     | <- Interior pages\n    +------------------------------------------------------------+\n    | Cell Pointer Array                                        | <- Low addr to High\n    |   - Each pointer: 2 Bytes                              |\n    |   - Sorted by key value                                 |\n    |                              v                               |\n    +------------------------------------------------------------+\n    | Unallocated Space                                        |\n    |                                                               |\n    |                                                               |\n    +-------------------------------------------------------------+\n    | Cell Content Area        ^                                | <- High addr to Low \n    |   - Densely arranged cells                                |\n    |   - May contain freeblock linked list                    |\n    |   - May contain fragment space                         |\n    +-------------------------------------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    +-----------------------------------------------------------+\n    | File Header (100 Bytes) - Page 1 Only               |\n    +------------------------------------------------------------+\n    | Page Header                                               | <- Fixed Position\n    |                                                               |\n    |   - Page type ......................................... 8 Bytes      | <- Leaf pages\n    |       - Page Type Flags ........................... 1 Byte     |\n    |       - First Freeblock Offset ................ 2 Bytes   |\n    |       - Number of Cells ............................. 2 Bytes   |\n    |       - Cell Content Area Start .............. 2 Bytes   |\n    |       - Fragmented Bytes Count ............. 1 Byte     |\n    |   - Right-most child pointer ................. 4 Bytes     | <- Interior pages\n    +------------------------------------------------------------+\n    | Cell Pointer Array                                        | <- Low addr to High\n    |   - Each pointer: 2 Bytes                              |\n    |   - Sorted by key value                                 |\n    |                              v                               |\n    +------------------------------------------------------------+\n    | Unallocated Space                                        |\n    |                                                               |\n    |                                                               |\n    +-------------------------------------------------------------+\n    | Cell Content Area        ^                                | <- High addr to Low \n    |   - Densely arranged cells                                |\n    |   - May contain freeblock linked list                    |\n    |   - May contain fragment space                         |\n    +-------------------------------------------------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zgr03W9TJ9bmmYk5Z7bdS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -186.82930053301766,
      "y": -76.2298392183709,
      "width": 690.8797607421875,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1441712990,
      "version": 393,
      "versionNonce": 856857758,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777861901224,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Page Type Flags\nBit:  7    6    5    4    3    2    1    0\n         +----+----+----+----+----+----+----+----+\n         |    |    |    |    | LE | LD | ZD | IK |\n         +----+----+----+----+----+----+----+----+\n                                    |    |    |    +-- PTF_INTKEY   (0x01)\n                                    |    |    +------- PTF_ZERODATA (0x02)\n                                    |    +------------ PTF_LEAFDATA (0x04)\n                                    +----------------- PTF_LEAF     (0x08)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Page Type Flags\nBit:  7    6    5    4    3    2    1    0\n         +----+----+----+----+----+----+----+----+\n         |    |    |    |    | LE | LD | ZD | IK |\n         +----+----+----+----+----+----+----+----+\n                                    |    |    |    +-- PTF_INTKEY   (0x01)\n                                    |    |    +------- PTF_ZERODATA (0x02)\n                                    |    +------------ PTF_LEAFDATA (0x04)\n                                    +----------------- PTF_LEAF     (0x08)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GmmU_MpfY17DOkJTvN8i7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -20.400736490885436,
      "y": 51.84244791666674,
      "width": 519.8197021484375,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2025807490,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 691480066,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777363219779,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cell Pointer Array:\n    +------+------+------+------+-----+\n    | Ptr0 | Ptr1 | Ptr2 | Ptr3 | ... |  (2 bytes each)\n    +------+------+------+------+-----+\n       |      |      |      |\n       v      v      v      v\n     Cell0  Cell1  Cell2  Cell3    (Actual positions vary)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cell Pointer Array:\n    +------+------+------+------+-----+\n    | Ptr0 | Ptr1 | Ptr2 | Ptr3 | ... |  (2 bytes each)\n    +------+------+------+------+-----+\n       |      |      |      |\n       v      v      v      v\n     Cell0  Cell1  Cell2  Cell3    (Actual positions vary)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HkzpXXTb6EYHryR0RcFC8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -198.44089230691566,
      "y": 184.30317515665087,
      "width": 675.5198974609375,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0I",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 755174786,
      "version": 381,
      "versionNonce": 31542238,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777862490168,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "   Cell Pointer Array: offset of key\n    +-------+------+-------+-------+-----+\n    | Ptr0 | Ptr1 | Ptr2 | Ptr3 | ...   |  (2 bytes each)\n    +-------+------+-------+-------+-----+\n       |       |       |      |\n       v      v       v      v\n     Cell0  Cell1  Cell2  Cell3    (Actual positions vary)\n    \n    好处：                                                                  \n    1. 插入时多数情况下只需移动 pointer array                               \n    2. cell 实体可以继续堆在页尾                                            \n    3. 降低大 payload 搬移成本                                              \n    4. 二分查找只在 pointer array 的“逻辑顺序”上做",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "   Cell Pointer Array: offset of key\n    +-------+------+-------+-------+-----+\n    | Ptr0 | Ptr1 | Ptr2 | Ptr3 | ...   |  (2 bytes each)\n    +-------+------+-------+-------+-----+\n       |       |       |      |\n       v      v       v      v\n     Cell0  Cell1  Cell2  Cell3    (Actual positions vary)\n    \n    好处：                                                                  \n    1. 插入时多数情况下只需移动 pointer array                               \n    2. cell 实体可以继续堆在页尾                                            \n    3. 降低大 payload 搬移成本                                              \n    4. 二分查找只在 pointer array 的“逻辑顺序”上做",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rxnXbPQtNPW90MWWRMcyr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1165.3840738932292,
      "y": 819.7200520833336,
      "width": 611.9595947265625,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
