      "updated": 1777861982284,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "  Record Payload ：不是“裸列数组”，而是 SQLite Record Format 编码后的整条记录 \n  +----------------------------------------------+                                              \n  | Record Header Size       (varint)        |                                              \n  | Serial Type 1            (varint)           |                                              \n  | Serial Type 2            (varint)          |                                              \n  | Serial Type 3            (varint)          |                                              \n  | ...                                             |                                             \n  +----------------------------------------------+                                              \n  | Column 1 Data            (bytes)         |                                              \n  | Column 2 Data            (bytes)        |                                              \n  | Column 3 Data            (bytes)        |                                              \n  | ...                                             |                                             \n  +----------------------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  Record Payload ：不是“裸列数组”，而是 SQLite Record Format 编码后的整条记录                                                                               \n  +----------------------------------------------+                                              \n  | Record Header Size       (varint)        |                                              \n  | Serial Type 1            (varint)           |                                              \n  | Serial Type 2            (varint)          |                                              \n  | Serial Type 3            (varint)          |                                              \n  | ...                                             |                                             \n  +----------------------------------------------+                                              \n  | Column 1 Data            (bytes)         |                                              \n  | Column 2 Data            (bytes)        |                                              \n  | Column 3 Data            (bytes)        |                                              \n  | ...                                             |                                             \n  +----------------------------------------------+",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
