    {
      "id": "HqCnGYUSB0Iv30_mqyOKE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 56.14956665039057,
      "y": 934.0234375,
      "width": 577.2399291992188,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0Z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1825702402,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 747012290,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777553373586,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• payload 如果太大，cell 并不会把全部数据都塞进本页，而是：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• payload 如果太大，cell 并不会把全部数据都塞进本页，而是：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tzdLzHkgWaDJhOdE_EQXq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 215.36958312988276,
      "y": 969.0234375,
      "width": 258.7998962402344,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 46700318,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 632317022,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777553373586,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• 先放一部分 Local Payload",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• 先放一部分 Local Payload",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AMC9JB8_4UjxTlGC_4JuL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 162.6095581054687,
      "y": 1004.0234375,
      "width": 364.3199462890625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0b",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1560703426,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 389879938,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777553373586,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• 最后再跟一个 4 字节 overflow 首页号",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• 最后再跟一个 4 字节 overflow 首页号",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EmgcG0QpQl5TqjShsODzf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535.0379111850156,
      "y": 966.0292198869815,
      "width": 793.1348401491887,
      "height": 149.68575363071255,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RYyWijsoKs6BntHHFvPgY"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0bV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1250780382,
      "version": 903,
      "versionNonce": 122045954,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777862018809,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• payload 如果太大，cell 并不会把全部数据都塞进本页，而是：                           \n    • 先放一部分 Local Payload                                                               \n    • 最后再跟一个 4 字节 overflow 首页号\n• SQLite 不是简单地“塞满本页再溢出”，而是要在 minLocal 和 maxLocal      \n  之间选一个局部大小，让 overflow 页尽量装满\n•  Total =  Local Payload On Btree Page + Overflow Payload On Overflow Pages",
      "fontSize": 19.958100484095006,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• payload 如果太大，cell 并不会把全部数据都塞进本页，而是：                                   \n    • 先放一部分 Local Payload                                                                  \n    • 最后再跟一个 4 字节 overflow 首页号\n• SQLite 不是简单地“塞满本页再溢出”，而是要在 minLocal 和 maxLocal      \n  之间选一个局部大小，让 overflow 页尽量装满\n•  Total =  Local Payload On Btree Page + Overflow Payload On Overflow Pages",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Qm45LyglHgu3ZWvJ3op56",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 528.40775362271,
      "y": 1148.8539515774075,
      "width": 1182.5830996134107,
      "height": 325.26499896596766,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RYyWijsoKs6BntHHFvPgY"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0c",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 389562114,
      "version": 735,
      "versionNonce": 676476354,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777862018809,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "  Overflow Page                                                           \n  +----------------------------------------------+                        \n  | Next Overflow Page No    (4 bytes)    | <- 0 表示链尾          \n  | Payload Chunk            (bytes)         | <- usableSize - 4      \n  +----------------------------------------------+                        \n                                                                          \n  Overflow Chain                                                          \n  +-----------------------------+      +-----------------------------+    \n  | Overflow Page #1        | ---> | Overflow Page #2       | ---> ...                                                                   \n  +-----------------------------+      +-----------------------------+    \n  | Next Page No             |       | Next Page No             |    \n  | Payload Chunk            |       | Payload Chunk            |    \n  +-----------------------------+      +-----------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20.01630762867493,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  Overflow Page                                                           \n  +----------------------------------------------+                        \n  | Next Overflow Page No    (4 bytes)    | <- 0 表示链尾          \n  | Payload Chunk            (bytes)         | <- usableSize - 4      \n  +----------------------------------------------+                        \n                                                                          \n  Overflow Chain                                                          \n  +-----------------------------+      +-----------------------------+    \n  | Overflow Page #1        | ---> | Overflow Page #2       | ---> ...                                                                   \n  +-----------------------------+      +-----------------------------+    \n  | Next Page No             |       | Next Page No             |    \n  | Payload Chunk            |       | Payload Chunk            |    \n  +-----------------------------+      +-----------------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
