      "updated": 1777862533633,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "  初始状态（紧凑）                                                        \n  +--------------------------------------------------+                    \n  | hdr | ptr array |       free       | cell | cell |                    \n  +--------------------------------------------------+                    \n                                                                          \n  删除若干 cell 后                                                        \n  +----------------------------------------------------+                    \n  | hdr | ptr array |   free   | freeblock |  cell   |                    \n  +----------------------------------------------------+                    \n                                                                          \n  继续插入/删除后                                                         \n  +-----------------------------------------------------+                    \n  | hdr | ptr array | free | frag | freeblock | cell |                    \n  +-----------------------------------------------------+                    \n                                                                          \n  调用 defragmentPage() 后                                                \n  +----------------------------------------------------------+                    \n  | hdr | ptr array |   unallocated spac   |cell |cell|cell|                   \n  +----------------------------------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  初始状态（紧凑）                                                        \n  +--------------------------------------------------+                    \n  | hdr | ptr array |       free       | cell | cell |                    \n  +--------------------------------------------------+                    \n                                                                          \n  删除若干 cell 后                                                        \n  +----------------------------------------------------+                    \n  | hdr | ptr array |   free   | freeblock |  cell   |                    \n  +----------------------------------------------------+                    \n                                                                          \n  继续插入/删除后                                                         \n  +-----------------------------------------------------+                    \n  | hdr | ptr array | free | frag | freeblock | cell |                    \n  +-----------------------------------------------------+                    \n                                                                          \n  调用 defragmentPage() 后                                                \n  +----------------------------------------------------------+                    \n  | hdr | ptr array |   unallocated spac   |cell |cell|cell|                   \n  +----------------------------------------------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
