      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777863129625,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "  SQLite Database File                                                    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 1                                                            |    \n  |  +------------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |  | 100-byte Database Header                             |  |    \n  |  +------------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |  | sqlite_schema root B-tree page                       |  |    \n  |  +------------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 2 : users table root page                              |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 3 : users leaf/interior page                            |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 4 : users leaf page                                      |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |        | Page Header                                         |  |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |        | Cell Pointer Array                                  |  |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |        | Unallocated / Freeblocks / Fragments         |   |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |        | Table Leaf Cell                                     |   |    \n  |        |   - payload size(varint)                           |   |    \n  |        |   - rowid(varint)                                    |  |    \n  |        |   - local payload                                    |  |    \n  |        |   - overflow pgno(optional)                       |  |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 5 : overflow page                                        |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 6 : freelist trunk page                                  |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 7 : freelist leaf page                                    |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  SQLite Database File                                                    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 1                                                            |    \n  |  +------------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |  | 100-byte Database Header                             |  |    \n  |  +------------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |  | sqlite_schema root B-tree page                       |  |    \n  |  +------------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 2 : users table root page                              |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 3 : users leaf/interior page                            |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 4 : users leaf page                                      |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |        | Page Header                                         |  |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |        | Cell Pointer Array                                  |  |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |        | Unallocated / Freeblocks / Fragments         |   |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  |        | Table Leaf Cell                                     |   |    \n  |        |   - payload size(varint)                           |   |    \n  |        |   - rowid(varint)                                    |  |    \n  |        |   - local payload                                    |  |    \n  |        |   - overflow pgno(optional)                       |  |    \n  |        +------------------------------------------------------+  |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 5 : overflow page                                        |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 6 : freelist trunk page                                  |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+    \n  | Page 7 : freelist leaf page                                    |    \n  +------------------------------------------------------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
